title: Tomorrowland 2014 : Music Will Unite Us Forever (2014) (320kbps)
description:
Tomorrowland 2014 : Music Will Unite Us Forever (2014) 

                Bigroom, Club, House. Electro | Kontor Records

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 03:38:29 | 513 Mb


This year, the legendary festival celebrates its 10th anniversary for the first time over two consecutive weekends! This event is of course celebrated with a unique compilation due! For the rich 3CD set of "Tomorrowland - Music Will Unite Us Forever" anniversary edition the star DJ Afrojack, Armin van Buuren, Steve Aoki and Yves V have contributed an exclusive mix for the CD1 & CD2 . The CD3 unites the biggest festival anthems from 10 years of "Tomorrowland" to a CD full of magical memories. The compilation is presented as a Deluxe Mediabook which impressively captures the 10-year history of the festival visually with photos.
